ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a wonderful class that will prepare you for grant writing, critical thinking, and preparing for your proposal.
Yes, because you at least have the opportunity to discuss your dissertation. Although not always as productive as I would hope, it offers more focus on your topic than other courses.
Yes, I will recommend it. It provides good opportunities for doctoral students to rethink their proposal by receiving comments on it.
N907 is a forum to give and receive feedback regarding our dissertation progress. I would recommend the course to help students develop their dissertation proposal.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I have submitted a grant and will be working on the first 2 chapters of my proposal over break!
You can focus on your dissertation and run ideas by classmates.

students received suggestions and comments directly from the instructor, and research advisers. all comments were based on student's proposal's weakness, which helped students refine and rethink their proposal. through this course, students could complete their research proposal more efficiently.
Helped to see how other students are progressing and develop my dissertation proposal.
